Electrum Neblio Wallet
he Neblio Blockchain Platform is a development platform built to simplify and accelerate the development and deployment of distributed applications on the Neblio Blockchain, and potentially other blockchain networks in the future. Difficulty and inadequate developer skillsets are seen as the major obstacles inhibiting the adoption of blockchain technology for developing distributed applications in the enterprise and business worlds.

Electrum based wallets, also known as “lite wallets”, provide a variety of benefits over the standard Neblio wallet. Electrum wallets offload much of the normal processing that a wallet must do up to servers that we run in the cloud, making them faster, in many cases more secure, and much lighter on your computer to run..
